{
  "stem": "1860.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, there are situations.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There are moments that I-- that I recall certain incidents.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For instance, friends still wonder why when I answer a telephone call, why I don't say hello as a matter or fact.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only, it's always hello?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like I'm wondering, who could it be?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I still have that feeling in me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's not natural the telephone is ringing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's always wondering, who could it be?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's-- and I-- I feel uncomfortable in large groups.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If there are gatherings, big gatherings I will go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Especially now, I feel it's my obligation to attend all those.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I don't feel very comfortable.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There is always-- that's when I go back to my wartime experiences.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think I am-- it-- it disturbs me in leading a normal life, but I am aware of it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like, I-- I don't, in particular, care-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I don't in particular for-- for women's luncheon, to be congregated together with women alone.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It always gets-- sends me back to-- brings me back to being together with a large group of women in a barrack.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know I have certain-- I don't know, these are maybe not phobias, but there are certain feelings that are left over from those days.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, since I was so young when-- when it happened to me, I would say that in order to keep on going, hope is extremely-- extremely important.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That-- that-- that keeps you alive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe because I am basically-- I am a warrior, but I am basically a-- an optimist.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] and, you know, like-- who-- who was it-- I think, if I may quote him-- John Milton who said that-- that a mind is place of its own.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
